frameDefinitions: An Agent attempts to achieve a Goal.
An Agent manipulates an Instrument in order to achieve a Purpose.
A Cognizer computes a Result on the basis of input Numbers by addition.
An Agent attempts to achieve a Goal using some Means.
An Agent makes use of a Means (either an action or a (system of) entities standing in for the action) in order to achieve a Purpose.
This frame involves stable Roadways which connect two stable Endpoints, the Source and the Goal.
